<p class="entry-meta"> &middot; <time class="entry-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="1999-11-08T20:46:21+07:00">November 8, 1999</time> &middot; </p></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><p>Legal advice was provided to Celestica by Tom Smee of Davies, Ward &amp; Beck and Lynn Toby Fisher of Kaye, Scholer, Fierman, Hays &amp; Handler, LLP (New York), and to the underwriters by Doug Marshall of Osler, Hoskin &amp; Harcourt LLP and Jason Lehner of Shearman &amp; Sterling.The fully marketed offering completed in November 1999 was the second financing completed by Celestica in 1999, the first offering having been done by way of a bought deal in March which raised approximately $340,000,000. &#x02026; <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/1999/11/celestica-inc-720m-offering-of-subordinate-voting-shares/" class="more-link">[Read more...] <span class="screen-reader-text">about Celestica Inc. $720M Offering of Subordinate Voting Shares</span></a></p></div><footer class="entry-footer"><p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-categories">Filed Under: Uncategorized</span> <span class="entry-tags"><a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/tesla-share-offering/" rel="tag" class="more">tesla share offering</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/advaxis-share-offering/" rel="tag" class="more">advaxis share offering</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/bjp-kerala-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">bjp kerala vote share</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/bjp-vote-share-2019/" rel="tag" class="more">bjp vote share 2019</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/bjp-vote-share-in-kerala-2019/" rel="tag" class="more">bjp vote share in kerala 2019</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/bjp-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">bjp vote share</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/bjp-50-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">bjp 50 vote share</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/trinamool-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">trinamool vote share</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/aiadmk-vote-share-2019/" rel="tag" class="more">aiadmk vote share 2019</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/admk-vote-share-in-tamilnadu/" rel="tag" class="more">admk vote share in tamilnadu</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/aiadmk-vote-share-in-2014/" rel="tag" class="more">aiadmk vote share in 2014</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/tamil-nadu-vote-share-2019/" rel="tag" class="more">tamil nadu vote share 2019</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/ldf-vote-share-in-kerala-2019/" rel="tag" class="more">ldf vote share in kerala 2019</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/labour-vote-share-2017/" rel="tag" class="more">labour vote share 2017</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/offer-quantity-in-share-market/" rel="tag" class="more">offer quantity in share market</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/pathanamthitta-vote-share-2014/" rel="tag" class="more">pathanamthitta vote share 2014</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/pathanamthitta-2014-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">pathanamthitta 2014 vote share</a>, <a href="https://www.lawbreakingnews.com/tag/brecon-and-radnorshire-vote-share/" rel="tag" class="more">brecon and radnorshire vote share</a></span></p></footer></article><div class="entry">
